DepreciationRecalculationReport is a BusinessTask
    owned by am

    Patterns
        implements ManualTransaction
        implements StaticJava
            is report for FinancialsViewer, AssetManager, ApplicationAdministrator, FinancialsProcessor, AssetAnalyst, Assets
                category is "Depreciation"
                report name is "RecalculateDepreciation"
			    Description
                    This report will calculate and display current depreciation values for included assets.
                    When run in update this report will update the depreciation for included assets.
                    It will not create journal entries for any adjusted depreciation.
            Reports
                DepreciationRecalculationReportReport

